# Gemini SDK Migration Guard

Use this file only to block legacy Gemini patterns during edits in `ai_audit/`.

For the canonical package, model, and initialization requirements, follow **`ai-audit-governance.mdc` section 2**.

## Blocked legacy patterns

- **Library:** `google-generativeai`
- **Pattern:** `genai.GenerativeModel()`
- **Decommissioned model IDs:** `gemini-1.5-flash`, `gemini-1.5-pro`, `gemini-1.0-pro`

## Enforcement action

If you see one of the blocked legacy patterns above, stop and migrate the code to the `google-genai` + `genai.Client(...)` flow defined in **`ai-audit-governance.mdc` section 2**.